title: Shocker Internet Drive In - Week 59: "Springtime For Starman - Part 2"

sources.title: Shocker Internet Drive In - Week 59: "Springtime For Starman - Part 2"
sources.description: As promised, we here at everyone's favorite haunt are happy to bring you the second half of our special Starman (aka Super Giant) quadruple feature. Once again, after the usual stuff, including a cartoon, we happily present the 3rd English movie "Attack From Space". Then, after a brief intermission, we offer up the final Starman feature - "Evil Brain From Outer Space".
